'''The Exchange''' was a semi-permanent business established by [[Thasca Knarr]] in one of the rooms of [[Exovar's Emporium]]. In addition to making money, Knarr planned to use The Exchange as a staging point for a mission to try and take over the Emporium to use as a base of operations for criminal activities.<ref name="WHSV">''[[Wretched Hives of Scum & Villainy]]''</ref>

